en-AU.name: COVID Facts
en-AU.description:
Ask for COVID Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

COVID Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch COVID Facts" or "Alexa, open COVID Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
